page.title: 08Clubs/Beaminster Youth Club
page.content: Quite a lot of children betwen the age of 10-14 go to Beaminster Youth Club.In the main building,there are three levels.On the top level there is room with table tennis and darts.Further down the corridor there is a room with a television.Down the stairs is the main room,with a Hi-Fi system,and also there is a pinball,space invaders,a pool table,a bar,and 2 Commodore 64's.In the hall they teach certain sports.There is also a video and piano.Opposite the pinball is a notice board where they inform you of trips they organize.
